rust, Tiffany & Co, Mangusta Yachts, XXII Carat, Luxhabitat, Palacio Versace, Emaar Hospitality Group, Hakkasan, Platinum Auction and many more. Heidi Mallace <img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-557386 aligncenter lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://i1.wp.com/businessday.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image8.jpeg?resize=406,406&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="406" height="406" data-srcset="https://i1.wp.com/businessday.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image8.jpeg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/businessday.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image8.jpeg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i1.wp.com/businessday.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image8.jpeg?resize=100%2C100&amp;ssl=1 100w, https://i1.wp.com/businessday.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image8.jpeg?resize=512%2C512&amp;ssl=1 512w, https://i1.wp.com/businessday.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image8.jpeg?w=700&amp;ssl=1 700w" sizes="(max-width: 406px) 100vw, 406px" data-recalc-dims="1"><img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-557386 aligncenter lazyload jetpack-lazy-image" src="https://i1.wp.com/businessday.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image8.jpeg?resize=406,406&amp;ssl=1" alt width="406" height="406" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-srcset="https://i1.wp.com/businessday.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image8.jpeg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/businessday.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image8.jpeg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i1.wp.com/businessday.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image8.jpeg?resize=100%2C100&amp;ssl=1 100w, https://i1.wp.com/businessday.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image8.jpeg?resize=512%2C512&amp;ssl=1 512w, https://i1.wp.com/businessday.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image8.jpeg?w=700&amp;ssl=1 700w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 406px) 100vw, 406px" data-lazy-src="https://i1.wp.com/businessday.ng/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/image8.jpeg?resize=406%2C406&amp;ssl=1&amp;is-pending-load=1" srcset=